            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I feel like this is the expected behavior. Try adding this to your config\n```lua\nvim.o.shellslash = true\n```\nAlso, what does this return?\n```vim\n:lua =vim.fs.normalize(vim.fn.fnamemodify([[C:\\Users\\]], ':p'))\n```\n(In Nvim 0.11, you will be able to use `vim.fs.abspath()` instead)",
